WWW-Scraper-ISBN-Siciliano_Driver
=================================

This distribution contains two Perl extensions for the ISBN search collection 
that is provided by WWW::Scraper::ISBN.

The drivers search for book information from the Siciliano online catalog from
www.siciliano.com.br.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules:

   LWP
   HTTP::Request::Common
   WWW::Scraper
   WWW::Scraper::ISBN
   WWW::Scraper::ISBN::Driver
   WWW::Scraper::ISBN::Record

